- 'categories' refers to the class names of boroughs;
- 'investigators' refers to users with the role labeled as 'researcher';
- 'access rights' refer to the permission levels held by users.

sql:
SELECT boroughs.name, borough_classes.class_name
FROM boroughs
INNER JOIN borough_classes ON boroughs.class = borough_classes.class_id;

